%section.py-20.px-4.sm:px-6.lg:px-8.bg-gray-50
  .max-w-7xl.mx-auto
    .text-center.mb-16
      %h2.text-4xl.md:text-5xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4
        Next-Gen Fleet Management: Your Dedicated Control Center
      %p.text-xl.text-gray-600
        Efficiency dictates profitability. Our dedicated partner dashboard is a powerful Fleet Management tool, designed to give you instant control and deep insights into your business performance. This technology automates lead generation and minimizes administrative overhead.

