            %h3.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-3
              Instant Listing Updates
            %p.text-gray-600.leading-relaxed
              Update pricing, availability, mileage, and high-resolution photos in real-time. Respond to market changes instantly.

          / Card 2 - Performance Monitoring
          .bg-white.p-8.rounded-xl.shadow-md.border.border-gray-100.hover:shadow-lg.transition-shadow
            .flex.items-start.mb-6
              .w-16.h-16.rounded-lg.flex.items-center.justify-center.flex-shrink-0{style: "background-color: #3A6363"}
