              Performance Monitoring
            %p.text-gray-600.leading-relaxed
              Access detailed analytics on views, clicks, lead conversion rates, and revenue generated per vehicle category. Identify your most profitable assets and regions.

          / Card 3 - Promotional Engine
          .bg-white.p-8.rounded-xl.shadow-md.border.border-gray-100.hover:shadow-lg.transition-shadow
            .flex.items-start.mb-6
              .w-16.h-16.rounded-lg.flex.items-center.justify-center.flex-shrink-0{style: "background-color: #00B4D8"}
